latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Just when my friends thought they knew me in and out 😉

These are the reactions I’ve always gotten whenever I’ve sang along to a song… many times Ive been told that I can sing and many times Ive been asked why I am not considering being a singer… singing by myself has always been therapeutic for me, not a day goes by where I don’t sing along when I listen to music… my dream and passion has always been acting so I wanted to pay all my attention to that until the pandemic gave me time and the resources to pursue this very personal and hidden love for singing ❤️ 
(Never be able to reach what the queen @adele can do but LOVE her music so… 🥰 )

This Video of me and my Co actor @vassilis_kookie has been going viral all over the world in the last 2 days in the Iranian community - accusing him of being the Head of Sepah in iran. 
We made this video to clarify that he only played the role of one and that we are just actors and the rumors aren’t true 😊 I guess that’s what happens when you are so extremely good and believable as an actor! 
But obviously we all should also use our common sense ;) we hope you like #TehranSeries

This is a snippet of the almost 4 min long Monologue in my last Series “Chutzpah” where I played a cam girl 🎥

It’s quite special to me, because I’ve always wanted to have a monologue in a film … which actor doesn’t ? 😬 And here I got to play a range of emotions… from happy to sad .. from being funny to sarcastic… from speaking in hindi all the way to English.. 

Chutzpah was very challenging for me in many ways because of the extreme looks- it had an oomph factor but none of those amazing looks and all that glam fills my heart with joy like doing a scene like this… and even though I didn’t have to sit in hair and make up for 3,5 hours for this scene , it was the most challenging one of all 🙌🏼 

Let me know if you liked the scene ?! 

اين يه تيكه كوچولويى از مونولوگ ٤ دقيقه CHUTZPAH ايى از سريال قبلي منه به نام 

، من توو اين سريال نقش يه كم گرل رو بازى ميكنم كه خانواده (پدر و مادرش )اش بهش اجازه نميدن كه هنرپيشه بشه و خيلى دوست داره كه هنرپيشه بشه و به همين دليل بايد يه جورايى پول در بياره تا بتونه در شهرى كه هست زندگى كنه تا بتونه به دنبال آرزوهاش بره!
نقش كم گرل رو بازى كردن خب براى من خيلى سخت بود و خيلى چالش برانگيز بود ولى فكر كنم بيشتر از اون همه صحنه ها اين صحنه و اين مونولوگ براى من سخت بود چون يك عالمه احساسات توو اين مونولوگ هست كه احساسات متغير داره از شاد تا ناراحت و حتى به گريه افتادن! و براى هر هنرپيشه ايى يه همچين مونولوگى بهتر و قشنگتره، متاسفانه با ترجمه فارسيش رو نداريم ولى اميدوارم كه خوشتون بياد.
❤️🤗
